  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Technology Guide pg. 48</em></p><p><strong>Price</strong> 8,000 gp</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> none; <strong>Weight</strong> 1 lb.</p><p><strong>Capacity</strong> 10; <strong>Usage</strong> 1 charge/hour</p><h2 class=\"framing\">Description</h2><p>This small, cylindrical device can be attached to the barrel of any firearm. When activated, it emits a low-power laser beam that paints a small red dot on the target. This effect grants the user a +1 circumstance bonus on all attack rolls made with that weapon. Further, a laser sight reduces the penalty for firing into melee by 2.</p><h2 class=\"framing\">Construction</h2><p><strong>Craft</strong> DC 24; <strong>Cost</strong> 4,000 gp</p><p>Craft Technological Item, production lab</p>",
